high_descs: Turn right, walk to the couch, turn right, walk a few steps, then turn right and face the coffee table.
Pick up the remote control that is closest to the blue plate on the coffee table.
Turn to the right, walk to the wall, then turn right again to walk up to the floor lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a remote control using the light of a lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the small coffee table in front of you.
Pick up the remote control which is closest to the blue object on the coffee table.
Turn right and walk to the tall lamp in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Examine a remote control by the light of a floor lamp.

high_descs: Turn right, go toward the couch, then turn right, step forward, and turn left to face the coffee table.
Pick up the remote nearest to you on the coffee table.
Turn right and then go to the lamp adjacent to the couch.
anns.task_desc: Examine a remote in the light of a lamp.
